name: Where do you go after you win
name_original: Where do you go after you win
description:
There is only one thing that is inevitable in every game. It might be sweet when achieved but still hurts when it happens. No wonder, both player and character are willing to do anything to postpone it. The truth is none of them knows where do you go after you win.

Controls:
arrows — movement / jump
space — attack / action
R — restart
esc — quit
